Nathalie Boutefeu https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathalie_Boutefeu 0 Nathalie Boutefeu (born 1968) is a French actress, film director and screenwriter. She has appeared in 40 films since 1990. She starred in the film The Butterfly's Dream, which was screened in the Un Certain Regard section at the 1994 Cannes Film Festival.
